{"tid":491163,"cid":21,"subCid":2,"title":"王菲〈冷戰〉原曲主唱人Tori Amos新碟 Native Invader","createTime":"2017-12-06T09:02:03.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-26T05:36:55.000Z","uid":40662,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"c7be7cf72c968efc686373d0e3634b3fcecb415a","tid":491163,"uid":40662,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-06T09:02:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://3.bp.blogspot.com/--RcyzWFIHFg/Wh2Uto0uJ4I/AAAAAAAAQD8/hQQ7FhhNBVs1i4xq-p_IJ6skVKJG1LjLACLcBGAs/s1600/63.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2F3.bp.blogspot.com%2F--RcyzWFIHFg%2FWh2Uto0uJ4I%2FAAAAAAAAQD8%2FhQQ7FhhNBVs1i4xq-p_IJ6skVKJG1LjLACLcBGAs%2Fs1600%2F63.jpg&h=7314fa95&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n大家仲記唔記得佢？曾得過八次Grammy Awards提名，王菲〈冷戰〉原曲〈Silent All These Years〉嘅主唱人Tori Amos。喺近年，有好多人都以為Tori支魔術棒已經徹底失去魔力，但喺今年九月，呢位諗法多多嘅音樂精靈又再次用行動去打破一眾樂迷對佢嘅質疑！有別於上一張碟嘅坦然豁達，今次呢張《Native Invader》所呈現出嚟嘅就係Dark &amp; Bright之間嘅反差！隨住Tori嘅生活過得越來越安逸，好似〈Wings〉、〈Cloud Riders〉、〈Up the Creek〉同〈Bang〉呢類咁有靈氣嘅作品都唔知有幾多年冇喺佢嘅唱片度出現過！特別係〈Cloud Riders〉嗰一陣層層遞進嘅陰森氣味就更比人有一種女巫回歸之感。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nTori Amos多張專輯以及新碟Native Invader的聽後感：<br />\n[url=<a href=\"http://timeischanging2013.blogspot.hk/2017/11/coco-me-201711.html]http://timeischanging2013.blogspot.hk/2017/11/coco-me-201711.html[/url]\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ftimeischanging2013.blogspot.hk%2F2017%2F11%2Fcoco-me-201711.html%5Dhttp%3A%2F%2Ftimeischanging2013.blogspot.hk%2F2017%2F11%2Fcoco-me-201711.html%5B%2Furl%5D&d=RrWYVrTiYs3SVwhRt8KSZBOFz4pMHIf1Ti9x7C0XgVU%3D&h=9803b067\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://timeischanging2013.blogspot.hk/2017/11/coco-me-201711.html]http://timeischanging2013.blogspot.hk/2017/11/coco-me-201711.html[/url]</a>"},{"pid":"afaf25681e22d6d12fe7032a729d4751a96b1933","tid":491163,"uid":40662,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-06T09:02:56.000Z","msg":"[quote]<img src=\"https://3.bp.blogspot.com/--RcyzWFIHFg/Wh2Uto0uJ4I/AAAAAAAAQD8/hQ